article_id:1621,category_name:Events,title_name:The Trick or Treasure! Facility Event Was Added to the Event Compendium!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/4d660958cb5bbba98b4b0971b64e5367.png,message:<div>The Trick or Treasure! facility event was added to the available events in the event compendium at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601013600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>In addition, with the changes made to the wyrmprint system, the content of certain endeavors and the Treasure Trade in the event compendium has been revised.</div><div><br></div><div>See here for details.</div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1605">Regarding Changes to the Wyrmprint System</a></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1622">Regarding Goodwill Gestures for Changes to the Wyrmprint System</a></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1176">See here for details about the event compendium.</a></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・All quests added this time are solo-only quests and cannot be played in co-op.</div><div>・More events will be made available in future updates.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1601013600,update_time1600944207